## ğŸ’» Code Standards

### TypeScript

- âœ… Use TypeScript for all code
- âœ… Avoid `any` types
- âœ… Define proper interfaces for component props
- âœ… Explicit return types on functions
- âœ… Use `import type` for type-only imports
- âœ… **Never use eslint-disable comments** - fix the underlying issue instead

### React

- âœ… Functional components with hooks only
- âœ… Component props must be typed
- âœ… Use `export default` for page components
- âœ… Import shadcn/ui from `@/components/ui/`
- âœ… Use Tabler Icons: `import { IconName } from "@tabler/icons-react"`
- âœ… Support `className` prop for customization

### Styling

- âœ… Tailwind CSS exclusively
- âœ… Dark mode via CSS variables
- âœ… Follow shadcn/ui patterns
- âœ… Use `cn()` from `src/lib/cn.ts` for class merging

## ğŸ—„ï¸ Database Rules

- âœ… Supabase environment vars: `REACT_APP_SUPABASE_*`
- âœ… Generate types: Run **db: generate types** task
- âœ… Use `.agent/LIVE/DATABASE_SCHEMA.md` for schema docs
- âœ… Seed data: `bun seed` or **seed: run** task

## ğŸš€ Development Commands

```bash
bun dev              # Start dev server
bun build           # Build for production
bun preview         # Preview prod build
bun lint            # Run Biomejs linter
bun format          # Format code
bun check           # Check code quality
bun type-check      # TypeScript check
bun seed            # Seed database
bun seed:clear      # Clear seed data
```

## ğŸ—„ï¸ Database Commands (VS Code Tasks)

```bash
# Run via VS Code: Ctrl/Cmd+Shift+P â†’ "Tasks: Run Task"
db: push schema      # Push pending migrations to Supabase
db: run migrations   # Run all pending migrations (--include-all)
db: pull schema      # Pull remote schema to local
db: generate types   # Generate TypeScript types from schema
db: reset local      # Reset local database
db: create migration # Create new migration file
```

### Running Migrations

1. Create migration: `supabase/migrations/XXX_name.sql`
2. Run via VS Code task: `db: push schema` or `db: run migrations`
3. Or via terminal: `npx supabase db push`


## ğŸ“ Common Patterns

### Page Component

```typescript
export default function HomePage() {
  return (
    <div className="space-y-4">
      <h1 className="text-4xl font-bold">Title</h1>
    </div>
  );
}
```

### Using Supabase

```typescript
import { supabase } from "@/lib/supabase";

const { data, error } = await supabase
  .from("table_name")
  .select("*");
```

### Using Tabler Icons

```typescript
import { IconCheck, IconX } from "@tabler/icons-react";

function Component() {
  return <IconCheck className="w-6 h-6 text-green-500" />;
}
```

## VS Code Tasks

Access via Cmd+Shift+P â†’ "Run Task":

- **dev** - Start development server
- **build** - Build for production
- **lint** - Run Biomejs linter
- **format** - Format all code
- **type-check** - Check TypeScript
- **db: push schema** - Push schema to Supabase
- **db: pull schema** - Pull schema from Supabase
- **db: generate types** - Generate TypeScript types
- **db: reset local** - Reset local database
- **seed: run** - Populate test data
- **seed: clear** - Clear all test data

## ğŸ“‹ Quality Checklist

Before committing:
- âœ… Run `bun lint` (fix all issues)
- âœ… Run `bun type-check` (no TypeScript errors)
- âœ… Run `bun build` (production build succeeds)
- âœ… Test in dev mode: `bun dev`
- âœ… Update `.agent/LIVE/PROGRESS` with changes
